We got a ground floor room which had TV with cable(BBC World News was nice for us Brits), huge bed, free WI FI, coffee maker but no fridge or microwave.	We also had a living room with couch, chair, desk/table with 2 side chairs and a large tv.	The room has a nice big flat screen tv and a refrigerator which is nice as I like to keep cold water and some beer in the room.	The bedroom is big & clean, the bed is super comfortable & king size, have a very good size TV, the bathroom was ok, but the bathtub was a bit small.